<!-- FULL_ARTICLE -->

Eight races: stat mods, class bitmap, skills, age/height/weight, infravision, hit die.

Tables below match Umoria `CHARACTER_RACES` in `src/data_player.rs` (mmspoilers-aligned). Class letters are Warrior Mage Priest Rogue Ranger Paladin. Lower perception (fos) is better. Saving throw tracks the device column.

--[ Stat mods & classes ]----------------------------------------------------

```
Race       STR INT WIS DEX CON CHR  Classes   XP%
Human       0   0   0   0   0   0   WMPRRP     0
Half-Elf   −1  +1   0  +1  −1  +1   WMPRRP    10
Elf        −1  +2  +1  +1  −2  +1   WMPRR     20
Halfling   −2  +2  +1  +3  +1  +1   WM R      10
Gnome      −1  +2   0  +2  +1  −2   WMPR      25
Dwarf      +2  −3  +1  −2  +2  −3   W P       20
Half-Orc   +2  −1   0   0  +1  −4   W PR      10
Half-Troll +4  −4  −2  −4  +3  −6   W P       20
```

XP% is the race experience penalty (see character/experience).

