```

--[ Body, infra, hit die ]---------------------------------------------------

Age is `base + 1d(mod)`. Infravision in feet (`infra_vision` × 10 in code). Hit die is racial HP base before class.

```
Race       age        Ht♂/Wt♂          Ht♀/Wt♀         infra  HD
Human      14+1d6     72+1d6/180+1d25  66+1d4/150+1d20    0'   10
Half-Elf   24+1d16    66+1d6/130+1d15  62+1d6/100+1d10   20'    9
Elf        75+1d75    60+1d4/100+1d6   54+1d4/80+1d6     30'    8
Halfling   21+1d12    36+1d3/60+1d3    33+1d3/50+1d3     40'    6
Gnome      50+1d40    42+1d3/90+1d6    39+1d3/75+1d3     40'    7
Dwarf      35+1d15    48+1d3/150+1d10  46+1d3/120+1d10   50'    9
Half-Orc   11+1d4     66+1d1/150+1d5   62+1d1/120+1d5    30'   10
Half-Troll 20+1d10    96+1d10/255+1d50 84+1d8/225+1d40   30'   12
```

